                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17830115-4-defend100 t17830115-4-punish38"></join>
               confined to hard labour two years in the house of correction
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the first Middlesex Jury before Mr. JUSTICE ASHURST.</p>
